{"tid":281813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"33%女59%男中學生曾看色情資訊","createTime":"2017-06-13T02:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T11:36:37.000Z","uid":78546,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb0497f3d3b4d5c7e275620231f49da8c513ea9","tid":281813,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170613/s00002/1497288555377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170613%2Fs00002%2F1497288555377&d=qeKQC1s%2B6N%2FZhKaNxDy3gp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2abdd812\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170613%2Fs00002%2F1497288555377&h=3446d354\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170613/s00002/1497288555377</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】智能電子產品普遍，不少學生已使用智能電話，青少年接觸色情資訊的途徑大增，研究發現分別有三成中學女生、六成中學男生表示曾看色情資訊，當中有五分之一男生一個月看15次或以上。但性交經驗的比例則微跌，有性交經驗者首次性交平均年齡與5及10年前一樣，維持在15歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n家計會執行總監范瑩孫表示，現今科技發達，青少年容易接觸色情資訊，當中包括文字、圖片或影片。<br />\n<br />\n五分一男生平均隔日觀看<br />\n<br />\n研究發現，有33%中學女生及59%男生稱有觀看色情物品，較2011年上升約5個百分點，當中更有五分之一男生表示過去1月個內觀看色情資訊15次或以上，相當於隔日就看一次。根據研究顯示，有關性交經驗的整體情况，只有1%至2% 中一至中二學生，與6%至7%的中三至中六學生有性交經驗，分別較2006年的4%及8%低；有性交經驗的中三至中六學生的首次性交平均年齡為15歲。<br />\n<br />\n有性交經驗比例微跌<br />\n<br />\n范瑩孫說青少年性交數字較以往低，可見觀看色情資訊數次多，不代表性交經驗會上升，但認為青少年一個月內觀看逾15次色情資訊的情况值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n對不同性傾向接納程度增<br />\n<br />\n研究同時發現受訪青少年對「女同性戀者、男同性戀者、雙性戀及跨性別行為」的接納程度有提高，當中有六成女受訪者及四成男受訪者，接受女同性戀者和男同性戀者；范瑩孫認為社會近年不時有這些議題的討論，令青少年的接納程度都有所上升。"},{"pid":"e82bad9b8c93353ccfd98c3b624a3d5ed85d263f","tid":281813,"uid":38671,"like":372,"dislike":0,"score":372,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"41%男生講大話"},{"pid":"1e99136e42ad036adecbfa9fde78823c309508e6","tid":281813,"uid":22310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>41%男生講大話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05d3cd62c9c29570c13d7e7823af483640d6da1","tid":281813,"uid":32298,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:41:00.000Z","msg":"平均性交年齡為15歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a9fae1f6bd3d0fdab54261c4521c19052ccfd6","tid":281813,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平均性交年齡為15歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc62bfebf227c1e43f44e3daa355da9df7184ab","tid":281813,"uid":531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平均性交年齡為15歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解冇報警撚"},{"pid":"12c0f679697eec148acb344dbcadb2672c3e68cc","tid":281813,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平均性交年齡為15歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解冇報警撚</blockquote><br />\n社工比連登仔高登仔屌死曬"},{"pid":"e927685efbe7d0a024c58b3576f042c1a586708c","tid":281813,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02